Canonical website:
  https://github.com/LanguageMachines/mbt/

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/LanguageMachines/mbt/archive/refs/tags/v3.11.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack mbt-3.11-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./mbt-3.11-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/mbt-3.11-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/mbt-3.11-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmbt2-3.11-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmbt-devel-3.11-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(mbt)
  /usr/bin/mbt.exe
  /usr/bin/mbtg.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/mbt.README
  /usr/share/doc/mbt/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/mbt/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/mbt/MAINTAINERS
